6:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Kissflow and Process Street share a solid foundation of core features including Visual Builder, Api Connections, Scheduling, Conditional Logic. Where Kissflow pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Code Support and Error Handling, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Process Street uniquely offers Ai Actions, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Kissflow holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Process Street scores 7/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Process Street comes in at a lower starting price of $100/mo, while Kissflow begins at $1500/mo. Neither platform offers a free plan, so you will need to budget for at least the starting tier from the beginning. Be sure to take advantage of any trial periods they may offer."}]]}]
